  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/e4c4267f25caf57a3aaf48419584827b.avif?t=1772086953\" width=388 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Rite of Eris</strong>, a <strong>free-to-play 3D survival roguelike</strong> inspired by the intensity of <i>Vampire Survivors</i>, the dynamic characters of <i>Paragon</i>, and the immersive worlds of <i>Hades</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the fractured realm of <strong>Eris</strong>, the Greek goddess of strife and discord, every journey is a test of adaptability and skill. Face endless waves of foes, uncover secrets, and carve your path through chaos in this ever-evolving rite of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All gameplay content is now completely free.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every character, map, game mode, and update can be unlocked through gameplay — no upfront purchase required.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/7c53b8737f8ab951cb158594a2bbdced.avif?t=1772086953\" width=388 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of survival in stunning cinematic 3D. Uncover hidden secrets, battle formidable foes, and navigate treacherous terrains. The world of Eris awaits you. Are you ready to accept the rite? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/b685a9554ee1a5d6bac62002e99fc614.poster.avif?t=1772086953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/b685a9554ee1a5d6bac62002e99fc614.webm?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/b685a9554ee1a5d6bac62002e99fc614.mp4?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free-to-Play with Full Unlock Progression</strong><br>• All characters, maps, game modes, and future updates are free.<br>• Progress through the world of Eris and unlock content naturally as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Survival Roguelike Combat</strong><br>• Engage in non-stop action as hordes of enemies flood the battlefield.<br>• Discover unique abilities and synergies to dominate waves of foes.<br>• Each character features distinct playstyles and tactical options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boss Encounters & Strategic Chaos</strong><br>• Face towering boss monsters that reshape the battlefield.<br>• Use their power against lesser enemies — if you can survive the cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand Your Look with Cosmetic DLC</strong><br>• Optional paid DLC skins and cosmetic sets are available to support development.<br>• These <strong>cosmetics do not affect gameplay</strong> and are purely for personalization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solo or Co-op Fun</strong><br>• Play alone or team up in local co-op to take on Eris’s challenges together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continual Growth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of <i>Rite of Eris</i> will continue to grow with new content added regularly.<br>The base game remains free, and new cosmetic packs will be released over time for players who want to support the project and customize their heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/596654ba3be87abc8bed6982b36d61a3.avif?t=1772086953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras_big/596654ba3be87abc8bed6982b36d61a3.webp?t=1772086953 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Currently includes 5 maps, 5 bosses, and 8 characters, but expanding to the full roster quickly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/2be0cab7150162b8900273395c13b518.avif?t=1772086953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras_big/2be0cab7150162b8900273395c13b518.webp?t=1772086953 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/fefebb81b0bbdb88c704d08fc2945a63.avif?t=1772086953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras_big/fefebb81b0bbdb88c704d08fc2945a63.webp?t=1772086953 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/822d545696e3742875e272f41795cf5e.avif?t=1772086953\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras_big/822d545696e3742875e272f41795cf5e.webp?t=1772086953 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on Rampage in the Ruins of Mystras.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/264a4fbc5a5287e65f3bc738e3e46af0.poster.avif?t=1772086953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/264a4fbc5a5287e65f3bc738e3e46af0.webm?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/264a4fbc5a5287e65f3bc738e3e46af0.mp4?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Poison Sevarog in the Tower of Hera.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/2de43f9f5c91abc5249ef46e2d3564a3.poster.avif?t=1772086953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/2de43f9f5c91abc5249ef46e2d3564a3.webm?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/2de43f9f5c91abc5249ef46e2d3564a3.mp4?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Terra in the Gladiator's Arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/939b02aafda540b49d6cf2b96d30d1dc.poster.avif?t=1772086953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/939b02aafda540b49d6cf2b96d30d1dc.webm?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779800/extras/939b02aafda540b49d6cf2b96d30d1dc.mp4?t=1772086953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
